Dependencies:
    Ubuntu and derivates:
        debhelper (>= 7)
        build-essential
        cmake
        automake
        autoconf
        pkg-config
        valac
        libgtk-3-dev
        libglib2.0-dev
        libjson-glib-1.0-0
        libjson-glib-1.0-0-dev
        
    Fedora and derivates:
        sudo dnf groupinstall "Development Tools"
        sudo dnf groupinstall "C Development Tools and Libraries"
        sudo dnf install gcc gcc-c++ gdb cmake automake autoconf pkgconf vala gtk3-devel json-glib-devel beesu

Installation:
    git clone https://github.com/gcleaner/gcleaner-vala.git
    cd gcleaner-vala
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..
    make
    sudo make install

Uninstall
    sudo make uninstall
